  m_Name: The Rival Orator
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Seed
  title: THE RIVAL ORATOR
  description: My Pontiff! An orator from a rival sect has taken a stand in the main
    plaza of the Ocularium and has begun to proselytize to all who will listen. This
    would not be a concern in itself, were it not for the fact that this particular
    speaker seems to possess a silver tongue. If we do not act to silence him, we
    risk the situation spiraling beyond our control!
